      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-500 pt-2">1. The service</h2>
      <p>
        Walk to Mordor ("the App") is a collaborative fitness tracker that converts your daily
        steps into progress along a shared journey with your group. By creating an account or using the
