      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-500 pt-2">10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these Terms? Please
        <a href="https://github.com/LHB410/one-does-not-simply-walk-into-morder/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
